==German==
===Etymology===
''zu'' "[[to]]" and a word related to "same", from Indo-European ''*samo-'' "[[same]]".
===Adverb===
'''zusammen'''
# [[together]]
===Usage notes===
*{{chemistry}} as an abbreviation, [[Z]], it is used to mean [[cis]] (see also [[entgegen]])
